        "text": "11\nSAC, Chicago\nAugust 8, 1947\nDirector, FBI\nFLYING DISCS\nRECORDED\nEX-66\nThe War Department has furnished this Bureau with the following\ntelegram dated July 5 at New York, New York:\n\"FOR FURTHER DETAILS CONCERNING FLYING DISKS SUGGEST"
